@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Admin Manages Appointments
actor Admin
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth Middleware (JWT)" as AUTH
database "Database (Neon)" as DB

== Load Appointment Dashboard ==

Admin -> UI: Open 'Appointments Management' page
UI -> API: GET /trl/appointments (JWT)

API -> AUTH: Verify JWT & role=Admin
AUTH --> API: Valid / Invalid

alt Invalid Token
    API --> UI: 401 Unauthorized
    UI --> Admin: Redirect to login
else Valid
    API -> DB: Fetch appointments (by status)
    API -> DB: Count attended
    API -> DB: Count absent
    API -> DB: Fetch upcoming appointments
    DB --> API: Return aggregated data
    API --> UI: 200 OK (dashboard data)
    UI --> Admin: Display appointment summary
    UI --> Admin: Display upcoming list
end



@enduml